Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.67,0:22:54.86,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}對如今的我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.01,0:22:59.72,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}そう キミの歌が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.01,0:22:59.72,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}對了 你的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.79,0:23:02.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}夜明けのように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.79,0:23:02.58,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}像拂曉般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:09.59,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}じんわり光をくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:09.59,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}將光明一點點地給予我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.81,0:23:14.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}塞ぎこんだ胸の奥に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.81,0:23:14.43,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}鬱結的胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:17.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}ちっぽけだけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:17.58,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}雖然只有極小的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.63,0:23:24.36,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}確かな希望 確かな希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.63,0:23:24.36,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}但是的確是希望 的確是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.41,0:23:27.36,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}僕にくれたから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.41,0:23:27.36,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}是你給予我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:30.85,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}もう迷わない 二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:30.85,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}我不會再迷茫了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:33.28,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}どんな未来も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:33.28,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}無論未來如何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:38.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}キミとなら逃げない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:38.18,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5}與你一起的話都不會再逃避
